## How much does HockeyStack cost in 2026?

HockeyStack doesn't publish exact pricing on its website — you have to talk to sales. Here's what we've gathered from Vendr data, review sites, and public reports.

### What does the base HockeyStack platform include?

The core HockeyStack platform includes:

| Feature | Included |
|---------|----------|
| **Multi-touch attribution** | Yes |
| **Buyer and account journey analytics** | Yes |
| **No-code funnel and cohort reporting** | Yes |
| **Cookieless tracking** | Yes |
| **CRM integrations** | HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive |
| **Ad network integrations** | LinkedIn, Google, Meta |
| **Marketing automation integrations** | Yes |

This base price gets you HockeyStack's core attribution and analytics capabilities. But the real cost is higher once you add modules.

### What are HockeyStack's add-on modules?

HockeyStack sells several capabilities as add-ons on top of the base platform:

| Add-On | What It Does |
|--------|-------------|
| **ABM / Account Intelligence** | Account-level tracking, intent signals, target account lists |
| **Nova AI (Sales Assistant)** | Account intelligence, stakeholder maps, account plans, auto-generated insights |
| **Odin AI (Analyst)** | Natural-language queries, automated reports, recommendations |
| **Data Warehouse Sync** | Export data to Snowflake, BigQuery, etc. |
| **Custom Agent Builder** | Build custom AI agents for GTM workflows (new 2025-2026) |

Each add-on is priced separately. A customer using the base platform + ABM + Nova could easily be paying $3,500-4,000+/month.

### What do most HockeyStack customers actually pay?

| Data Point | Amount | Source |
|------------|--------|--------|
| Median annual contract | ~$28,000/yr (~$2,333/mo) | Vendr marketplace data |
| Base platform | ~$2,200/mo | Multiple review sites |
| Historical entry (Dec 2023) | $1,399/mo for up to 10K unique visitors | Factors.ai comparison |

