### 1. Dreamdata — B2B on a Budget ($750/mo)

Dreamdata offers similar B2B attribution features at roughly one-third the price. Free tier for evaluation, transparent pricing, and best-in-class journey visualization.

**Why consider over HockeyStack:** $750/mo vs $2,200/mo for core B2B attribution. Free tier to evaluate. Better journey visualization.

**Why stick with HockeyStack:** HockeyStack bundles analytics, surveys, and AI agents. Faster to deploy (~2 weeks). Better if you want all-in-one.

Read more: [Dreamdata Pricing](/articles/dreamdata-pricing) | [Dreamdata Review](/articles/dreamdata-review)

