### 3. Factors.ai — Affordable B2B ($399/mo)

AI-powered B2B attribution at roughly one-fifth of HockeyStack's price. Account identification, multi-touch attribution, and path analysis included.

**Why consider over HockeyStack:** ~82% cheaper. AI-powered insights. Faster setup.

**Why stick with HockeyStack:** HockeyStack has deeper analytics, bundled surveys, and the AI GTM agent platform. Factors.ai is more focused on core attribution.

### 4. Bizible (Adobe Marketo Measure) — Enterprise Salesforce

Enterprise standard for Salesforce-native B2B attribution. Custom pricing.

**Why consider over HockeyStack:** Deepest native Salesforce integration. Built for enterprise ABM and governance.

**Why stick with HockeyStack:** HockeyStack is faster to deploy and more modern. Bizible requires 3-6 months of implementation.

### 5. GA4 — Free But Limited

Google Analytics 4 is free and includes basic attribution. Not a HockeyStack replacement, but a starting point.

**Why consider over HockeyStack:** Free. Immediate setup. Good enough for basic channel-level measurement.

**Why stick with HockeyStack:** GA4 has no B2B features, no account-level attribution, no CRM integration.

