## Should you pay for HockeyStack or use an alternative?

HockeyStack is a powerful all-in-one GTM platform — but at ~$2,200/mo base plus add-ons, it's a significant investment. The median $28,000/year contract makes sense for Series B+ B2B companies who can consolidate multiple tools into HockeyStack.

For teams who primarily need attribution (not the full GTM intelligence suite), Dreamdata ($750/mo), mbuzz ($29-299/mo), and Factors.ai ($399/mo) deliver core attribution capabilities at a fraction of the cost.

